text: Trashiyangtse District is one of the 20 districts in Bhutan. The administrative centre is Trashiyangtse. Bumdeling Wildlife Sanctuary is in the district. There are eight village blocks: *Bumdeling Gewog *Jamkhar Gewog *Khamdang Gewog *Ramjar Gewog *Toetsho Gewog *Tomzhangtshen Gewog *Trashiyangtse Gewog *Yalang Gewog Category:Districts of Bhutan
title: Trashiyangtse District
